s2d.geom

Class ShapeData

  • java.lang.Object
    • s2d.geom.ShapeData

  • public class ShapeData
extends java.lang.Object
    An object meant to store any shape that can be made in java. The main purpose of this object is for raycasting, but other uses will be added soon.
    In the raycaster is saves it from doing a lot of calculations on the spot.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    RayCaster
